# Web dashboard env (Vite). Copy to web/.env.local (gitignored) and fill in.
#
# P2 — operator route gate. The dashboard sends this as X-Operator-Key on every
# request to the operator routes (/campaigns, /payouts, /partnerships,
# /observability, /manual-queue, /workflows, /creators, /uploads, /queues). It
# MUST match OPERATOR_API_KEY in the server .env. Leave blank for local dev
# against an ungated server (the server is open-when-unset there too). NOTE: this
# key ships in the browser bundle — fine for the single-operator model (only
# Pluvus loads this dashboard), it is NOT per-user auth.
VITE_OPERATOR_API_KEY=
